about.summary: Provides a 'tbl_ts' class (the 'tsibble') for temporal data in an data- and model-oriented format. The 'tsibble' provides tools to easily manipulate and analyse temporal data, such as filling in  time gaps, aggregating over calendar periods, and etc.

name: r-tsibble
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.8.6" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-tsibble
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/tsibble_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/tsibble/tsibble_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 72ad15d05cb0819d2a7d20abb8219941ef8629501d596d643f8865ea1ccfa4ee

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-anytime >=0.3.1
    - r-dplyr >=0.8.1
    - r-lifecycle
    - r-lubridate >=1.7.0
    - r-purrr >=0.2.3
    - r-rlang >=0.2.0
    - r-tibble >=2.0.1
    - r-tidyselect
    - r-vctrs >=0.2.0
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-anytime >=0.3.1
    - r-dplyr >=0.8.1
    - r-lifecycle
    - r-lubridate >=1.7.0
    - r-purrr >=0.2.3
    - r-rlang >=0.2.0
    - r-tibble >=2.0.1
    - r-tidyselect
    - r-vctrs >=0.2.0

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('tsibble')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('tsibble')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://tsibble.tidyverts.org
  license: GPL-3
  summary: Provides a 'tbl_ts' class (the 'tsibble') for temporal data in an data- and model-oriented
    format. The 'tsibble' provides tools to easily manipulate and analyse temporal data,
    such as filling in  time gaps, aggregating over calendar periods, and etc.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - philip-khor
